headline.print_headline: Vekic Beats Cibulkova for 1st WTA Title
headline.main: Vekic Beats Cibulkova for 1st WTA Title

lead_paragraph: Seventh-seeded Donna Vekic of Croatia clinched her first WTA title on Sunday after beating top-seeded Dominika Cibulkova of Slovakia 5-7, 7-5, 7-6 (4) in the Malaysian Open final.
